  "title": "Delicious Festive Mexican Toor Dal Tacos",
  "description": "A festive Mexican dish featuring toor dal, stir-fry, and anti-inflammatory friendly ingredients, with a salty and fluffy texture. This dish is perfect for special occasions and can be served as a main course.",
