  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat and saute the onion and garlic until softened.",
    "Add the bell pepper and cook until tender.",
    "Add the toor dal, taco seasoning, and water to the pan, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes or until the dal is cooked and fluffy.",
    "Warm the tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by spooning the dal mixture onto a tortilla and topping with avocado, cilantro, and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
